</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>The <em><strong>intrinsic <link href="erct-0010.xml" type="local" addr="erct-0010" title="Path object">path object</link></strong></em> on a type <tex>A</tex>, written <tex>A ^{=}</tex>, is defined by setting <tex>x \cong _{ A ^{=} } y : \equiv   \mathopen {} \left ( x = y \right ) \mathclose {}</tex> and <tex>1_{ x }  : \equiv   \mathsf {refl}</tex>.</p>
 
   
   
 
